<p style="color:#000;margin:0 0 1em">
  I’m Jeremy Daer with the Basecamp security team.
    (We’re the creators of Highrise.)
</p>

<p style="color:#000;margin:0 0 1em">
  As part of our work to keep your account secure, <strong>we’ve removed an unsafe password from your Highrise account</strong>. You’ll need to set up a brand new password to log in.
</p>

<p style="color:#000;margin:0 0 1em">
